race.comment: END OF TUNNEL (1) was out of the placings last time when sixth at this track (24.47) but scored five back at this track (24.17). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Can bounce back. ASTON CHEROKEE (2) box seated before sticking on well to finish 0.8 lengths away in second (24.43) at this track in a Mix 5 over 407m. Can feature again. ASTON HAYES (6) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 407m behind Impactful (24.41) in a Grade 4. Was in the money prior to that. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. WHERE'S MY BEER (7) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.
